  "detailed_description": "<h1>Planet of Lana II: Children of the Leaf - OUT NOW!</h1><p>Planet of Lana II follows Lana and Mui as they step into a new chapter in a changing world.<br>On their home planet, new technology brings progress but also stirs greed and conflict. As harmony begins to shift, Lana and Mui are drawn into a journey to uncover long-buried truths about their world and themselves.<br><br>Their journey grows into a bigger, deeper cinematic adventure built on everything players loved about Planet of Lana.<br><br>Visit the Planet of Lana II Steam page to learn more.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/97ae919989de52aa47edb60e7435eaa3.poster.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/97ae919989de52aa47edb60e7435eaa3.webm?t=1772728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/97ae919989de52aa47edb60e7435eaa3.mp4?t=1772728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A planet that used to be a place of undisturbed balance between human, nature, and animal has now become something else entirely.  </p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The disharmony that had been in the making for hundreds of years has finally arrived in the form of a faceless army. But this is not a story about war. This is a story about a vibrant, beautiful planet –and the journey to keep it that way. </p><br><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique companion-based gameplay. <br></li><li>Solve puzzles with diverse challenges and quirky twists. <br></li><li>Carefully navigate dangerous situations using stealth and wit.<br></li><li>Use your reflexes and survive challenging action sequences. <br></li><li>Discover an epic story that stretches across galaxies and centuries. <br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/e15d044e42fad43290024556441a2f02.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=134 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/e264ab9a22229c89c5fb511f1cbfbb60.poster.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/e264ab9a22229c89c5fb511f1cbfbb60.webm?t=1772728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/e264ab9a22229c89c5fb511f1cbfbb60.mp4?t=1772728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/add274b1d169eb97d89d5ca9b02f5023.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=134 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/1c13f3d6435f36c0dc476541018facb4.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=300 /></span> </p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608230/extras/914f633e04034793790e4d21f0984711.avif?t=1772728759\" width=616 height=134 /><